The Radicons exited the People's Base and walked along through a forest arg=
uing. "Technical wrestling is the best style of wrestling there is!" Strana=
to said aloud. "Forget all that junk, when your in the heat of battle it do=
esn't matter what you do, you jusst beat the opponent up!" Scamrock said. S=
tronghold didn't say anything, he just picked up a boulder above his head a=
nd slammed it down. He proved his point. Train Wreck shook his finger. "Nop=
e, submissions have always been the best since the beginning of time!" He s=
aid. "You need to go high risk to win!" Airbomber said. Arrow laughed at th=
em all. "To win you have to do whatever is possible, rip out their eyes if =
you have to!" Arrow said. They walked off arguing through the forest...

Dr=
acona set out once again, this time dragging plintissa with her. "That bot =
joined the Predacons instead of us, shows how good we're progressing!" Drac=
ona said. "Plintissa was thinking about Suukie and the wonderland they were=
 in together, and Dracona didn't like it. "We have to concintrate on winnin=
g." Dracona said. Plintissa shrugged and walked along by the lake with Drac=
ona...

Suukie snoozed, his core conciousness turned off...

Sinesis was ex=
ploring the mountainside with sinister, telling him the advantage of deceit=
 while Sinister looked for stuff that was a threat that he could kill...

ightmare kissed Gangon and he fainted. Lightmare laughs...
